    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and add the<strong> pizza bases</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>tomato base</strong> between the <strong>pizza bases</strong> and spread it evenly all over them with the back of a spoon</p><p>Dollop the<strong> creamy base</strong> over the pizza bases and lightly swirl into the tomato base</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
