          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the bases with the<strong> torn mozzarella</strong></p><p>Tear over the <strong>‘Nduja</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Top with the<strong> chopped Tenderstem broccoli </strong>and add a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
